decision_details:
- The proposal made by Hon. Malik Samarawickrema, the Minister of Development Strategies and International Trade, to sign the following two MoU during the forthcoming State Visit of H.E. the President to Bangladesh, with a view to deepening and   diversifying cooperation in trade and  Investment between Sri Lanka and Bangladesh was approved by the Cabinet: 

*	MoU on Economic Cooperation between the two countries;

*	MoU on Investment Cooperation between the Investment Development Authority of Bangladesh and the Board of Investment of Sri Lanka.
